險"},{"pid":"af2d63730ed7806ae57811a45fb5b90ae7d83a15","tid":523272,"uid":154841,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07f11263e7f27cb3ea62352bb9e2e0c4d553064f","tid":523272,"uid":70118,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48f64af1219154730d61f134407c31660c0d9bf9","tid":523272,"uid":11578,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T13:28:55.000Z","msg":"岀艇一定會用背落<br />\n大船就會用跨步式落水<br />\n<br />\n利申: Adv"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T13:37:11.000Z","msg":"原因係?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T13:43:21.000Z","msg":"因為大船，一般會偏高身（做背落會有一定難度，同埋會容易反多左）<br />\n艇因為比較貼緊身，背落容易啲，而家艇一般唔會有空間俾你走動，所以出艇多數係著好晒坐定定，去到落水位，就個人背落，直接落水。"},{"pid":"471cf95a241165f4ee3464daecf0f37f58c81423","tid":523272,"uid":8595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07f11263e7f27cb3ea62352bb9e2e0c4d553064f","tid":523272,"uid":70118,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48f64af1219154730d61f134407c31660c0d9bf9","tid":523272,"uid":11578,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T13:28:55.000Z","msg":"岀艇一定會用背落<br />\n大船就會用跨步式落水<br />\n<br />\n利申: Adv"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T13:37:11.000Z","msg":"原因係?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T13:43:25.000Z","msg":"一黎艇仔未必有個平台位俾你誇步落水, 二黎頭先巴打都講左落水果下會搞到部艇好搖。<br />\n<br />\n利申: 9up"},{"pid":"382699da698038cd2901fc0b62e6a8edf4aa547a","tid":523272,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":30,"score":-29,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T13:44:31.000Z","msg":"成班on9<br />\n<br />\n因為潛水員之前暈船浪<br />\n倒後落中和返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b6c5fbc7874b97d1965b3142ce91c586bfcf7f2","tid":523272,"uid":75088,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T13:45:46.000Z","msg":"我女 背住個氧氣樽 根本連行都覺得困難<br />\n好難跳落水<br />\n係船上面 啲教練會幫手拓一拓起個樽<br />\n比我坐船邊 就可以背面落水 爽好多<br />\n<br />\n台灣就行落水 辛苦到仆街<img src